MELUSUN TERMS OF USE
Last Updated: February 10, 2026

PLEASE READ THESE TERMS OF USE CAREFULLY. BY DOWNLOADING, INSTALLING, ACCESSING, OR USING THE MELUSUN MOBILE APPLICATION ("APP"), YOU AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THESE TERMS. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE, DO NOT USE THE APP.

1) ABOUT MELUSUN Melusun ("we," "us," or "our") provides an application that offers astrology/zodiac-related experiences and AI-assisted content. The App is provided for personal, non-commercial use unless we expressly agree otherwise.

2) ELIGIBILITY You must be able to form a binding contract under applicable law to use the App. If you are under the age required to consent to data processing in your country, you may use the App only with parental/guardian consent where required.

3) IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER (ENTERTAINMENT & INFORMATIONAL PURPOSES) The App may provide content related to astrology, personality insights, emotional reflection, and AI-generated suggestions. ALL CONTENT IS PROVIDED FOR ENTERTAINMENT AND INFORMATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY.

The App does NOT provide medical, mental health, legal, financial, or other professional advice.

Do not rely on the App for decisions that could cause harm (including health, safety, legal, or financial decisions).

You are solely responsible for how you use the App and any actions you take based on the App’s content.

4) AI-GENERATED CONTENT The App includes features that generate content using artificial intelligence ("AI Content").

AI Content may be inaccurate, incomplete, outdated, or inappropriate.

AI Content is not guaranteed to be correct, unique, or suitable for your specific situation.

You should independently evaluate AI Content before relying on it.

5) DEVICE-ONLY STORAGE; NO ACCOUNT The App does not require account registration. Data you enter (such as preferences, inputs, or results) is primarily stored locally on your device. We do not provide cloud backups or cross-device syncing unless explicitly stated within the App.

6) THIRD-PARTY SERVICES (INCLUDING AI PROVIDERS) To provide AI features, the App may send certain user-provided text inputs to third-party AI service providers for processing and to generate outputs. These providers may process data according to their own terms and policies. We do not control third-party services and are not responsible for their availability, security, or practices.

7) ACCEPTABLE USE You agree not to:

Use the App in violation of any law or regulation.

Attempt to interfere with, disrupt, or gain unauthorized access to the App or related systems.

Reverse engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract source code except where permitted by law.

Use the App to create, request, or distribute illegal, harmful, or abusive content.

8) INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY The App, including its design, text, graphics, logos, and other content (excluding your inputs), is owned by Melusun or its licensors and protected by intellectual property laws. You may not copy, modify, distribute, sell, or lease any part of the App without our permission.

9) UPDATES AND CHANGES We may modify, update, or discontinue any part of the App at any time. We may also update these Terms. Continued use after updates means you accept the revised Terms.

10) LIMITATION OF LIABILITY TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW:

MELUSUN WILL NOT BE LIABLE FOR INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, PROFITS, OR GOODWILL.

MELUSUN’S TOTAL LIABILITY FOR ANY CLAIM RELATED TO THE APP WILL NOT EXCEED THE AMOUNT YOU PAID TO USE THE APP (IF ANY) IN THE 12 MONTHS BEFORE THE EVENT GIVING RISE TO LIABILITY.

