MELUSUN PRIVACY POLICY
Last Updated: February 10, 2026

This Privacy Policy explains how Melusun ("we," "us," or "our") handles information in connection with the Melusun mobile application ("App").

1) SUMMARY

No account required.

Primarily device-only storage.

Certain text inputs may be sent to third-party AI providers to generate responses.

We do not sell personal information.

2) INFORMATION YOU PROVIDE You may choose to enter information such as birth details, preferences, journal-like notes, prompts, or other text ("User Inputs"). Unless otherwise stated, these are stored locally on your device.

3) DEVICE-ONLY STORAGE (NO CLOUD SYNC BY DEFAULT) The App is designed to store data locally on your device. We do not automatically upload your data to a Melusun server for storage. If you delete the App or clear its storage, your local data may be permanently deleted.

4) AI PROCESSING (THIRD-PARTY PROVIDERS) If you use AI features, the App may transmit certain User Inputs to third-party AI service providers to generate outputs.

We send only what is needed to fulfill your request.

Transmission is intended to occur over encrypted connections (e.g., HTTPS).

We do not intend to permanently store the content of AI requests on Melusun servers unless explicitly stated in the App.

IMPORTANT: Third-party AI providers may process or retain data according to their own policies. Please review the policies of the relevant provider(s) if you have concerns.

5) INFORMATION WE DO NOT COLLECT (BY DEFAULT) We do not require:

Name, phone number, or account credentials

Government identifiers

Precise location (GPS)

6) CHILDREN’S PRIVACY The App is not directed to children under 13 (or the minimum age required in your country). We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

7) SECURITY We use reasonable safeguards to protect information. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure. You are responsible for securing your device (e.g., passcode).

8) YOUR CHOICES

You can delete local data by uninstalling the App (or clearing the App’s storage).

You can stop using AI features at any time by not submitting prompts.

9) CHANGES TO THIS POLICY We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will update the "Last Updated" date above. Continued use of the App after changes means you accept the updated policy.

10) CONTACT Questions or requests: Email: zenentw@gmail.com
